Professor,<br><br>
Thanks, for checking out my page.<br><br>
The greatest rewards are the favorable comments I receive  from vets, such as yourself, and the requests for more info which I receive from students and teachers.<br><br>
Since coming on line, I have learned that the best approach to the Vietnam War is to try to understand ALL facets and sides. I have no agenda other than to present information. Instead of editorializing, I would much rather let the reader make up his own mind and form his own opinion regarding the HISTORY of the war in Vietnam. It is history now, as we all know. <br><br>
As for the Packers, it is quite hard for this growling Chicago Bear fan to be objective about them! For now, a &quot;wait til next year&quot;, will have to suffice.<br><br>
Thanks again for you comments.<br><br>
Peace,<br><br>
Tom<br><br>

